{"word":"G3152 - μάταιος - mátaios - mat'-ah-yos - Vain","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μάταιος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">mátaios</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">mat'-ah-yos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Vain</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"வீணான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"useless, to no purpose"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From the base of <a href=\"#/G3155 - μάτην - mátēn - mat'-ane/3155\">G3155</a>; <i>empty</i>, that is, (literally) <i>profitless</i>, or (specifically) an <i>idol:</i> - vain, vanity.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3150/3150\">G3150</a>, <a href=\"#/G3151/3151\">G3151</a>, <a href=\"#/G3152/3152\">G3152</a>, <a href=\"#/G3153/3153\">G3153</a>, <a href=\"#/G3154/3154\">G3154</a>, <a href=\"#/G3155/3155\">G3155</a>"}]}